    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132690/extras/3baa5a3e4531bf4a454fdd8d37e9a125.avif?t=1749282351\" width=616 height=72 /></span>随着其他国家之间的战争的逐步升级，被夹在这些国家当中的莫多纳也迎来了最危险的时刻。在内忧外患的局势之中，莫多纳的人民深受重税和兵役之害，苦不堪言。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在国家面临生死存亡之时，骑士团长塞里斯与自己青梅竹马的妹妹玛雅，还有身为公主的艾丽西亚，三人挺身而出，打算共同拯救他们的国家免遭亡国厄运。三人发誓要消灭凶恶的怪物，敌国的军队和内部的叛徒，夺回属于莫多纳的安宁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英雄们究竟能否力挽狂澜，在保持自身清白的前提下完成无比艰巨的任务呢？在这部幻想RPG大作当中一睹为快吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132690/extras/34164a458eaedb76a27be9d92d8e5596.avif?t=1749282351\" width=616 height=72 /></span>您可以通过回合制战斗让游戏的主角们变得更加强大，学会全新的技能，并且使用华丽的组合技消灭敢于挡在他们面前的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您在游戏中做出的选择，还有与其他角色的好感度，除了会影响到当下的状况以外，还会影响游戏的走向甚至最终的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132690/extras/4d380f39ef6316aa2a9f2d09c2d3f969.avif?t=1749282351\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132690/extras/c0e968ac11ac639c5df41ad9f8626627.avif?t=1749282351\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132690/extras/1d28a6ea4b491e41522624b5d25e9897.avif?t=1749282351\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132690/extras/4f062e5e37e8dfe96c986695282425a5.avif?t=1749282351\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132690/extras/454397ffde6cc75172ccc59ada78055b.avif?t=1749282351\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>幻想风RPG</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场战斗都能让英雄们积累更多的经验，获得更强大的装备，以面对更加严峻而又刺激的挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精心绘制的插画</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这部作品的剧情CG以及战斗CG，皆为经验丰富的画师精心绘制之作，一切都是为了能让屏幕前的您拥有最顶级的游戏体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可供探索的庞大游戏世界</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这部作品中，战斗并不是唯一的主旋律。在战斗之余，您可以跟随任务的进度探索大陆上的每一个部分，用各种支线任务来舒缓紧张的神经！</p>",
